HEADWORD: Multivalvular
<hw>Mul`ti*val"vu*lar</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Multi-</ets> +
<ets>valve</ets>, <ets>valvular</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>multivalve</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Having many
