<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Many-valved; having more than two
valves; -- said of certain shells, as the chitons.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Multiversant</ent>⟦br⟧
